quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  8,49,‘IDH JEKULUL-MUNAFIKUNE WEL-LEDHINE FI KULUBIHIM MEREDUN GARRE HA’UULA’ DINUHUM WE MEN JETEWEKKEL ‘ALA ELLAHI FE’INNALL-LLAHE ‘AZIZUN HEKIMUN
  8,50,WE LEW TERA ‘IDH JETEWEFFAL-LEDHINE KEFERUL-MELA’IKETU JEDRIBUNE WUXHUHEHUM WE ‘EDBAREHUM WE DHUKU ‘ADHABEL-HERIKI
  8,51,DHALIKE BIMA KADDEMET ‘EJDIKUM WE ‘ENNEL-LAHE LEJSE BIDHELLAMIN LIL’ABIDI
  8,52,KEDE’BI ‘ALI FIR’AWNE WEL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIHIM KEFERU BI’AJATI ELLAHI FE’EHADHEHUMU ELLAHU BIDHUNUBIHIM ‘INNALL-LLAHE KAWIJUN SHEDIDUL-’IKABI
  8,53,DHALIKE BI’ENNEL-LAHE LEM JEKU MUGAJJIRÆN NI’METEN ‘EN’AMEHA ‘ALA KAWMIN HETTA JUGAJJIRU MA BI’ENFUSIHIM WE ‘ENNEL-LAHE SEMI’UN ‘ALIMUN
  8,54,KEDE’BI ‘ALI FIR’AWNE WEL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIHIM KEDHDHEBU BI’AJATI RABBIHIM FE’EHLEKNAHUM BIDHUNUBIHIM WE ‘EGREKNA ‘ALE FIR’AWNE WE KULLUN KANU DHALIMINE
  8,55,‘INNE SHERRE ED-DEWABBI ‘INDEL-LAHIL-LEDHINE KEFERU FEHUM LA JU’UMINUNE
  8,56,EL-LEDHINE ‘AHEDTE MINHUM THUMME JENKUDUNE ‘AHDEHUM FI KULLI MERRETIN WE HUM LA JETTEKUNE
  8,57,FE’IMMA TETHKAFENNEHUM FIL-HERBI FESHERRID BIHIM MEN HALFEHUM LE’ALLEHUM JEDHDHEKKERUNE
  8,58,WE ‘IMMA TEHAFENNE MIN KAWMIN HIJANETEN FANBIDH ‘ILEJHIM ‘ALA SEWA’IN ‘INNALL-LLAHE LA JUHIBBUL-HA’ININE